{"tid":1378720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致所有公務員","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T00:17:56.000Z","uid":60563,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"944caac9dcee5e67007a85636f9a1752106f470d","tid":1378720,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"唔理你有冇份拎張委任證出黎表態都好<br />\n我想講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢場抗爭如果失敗，你地個鐵飯碗冇可能會保得住</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為縮係張memo紙後面就可以有後路保住你份工<br />\n中共一定會用盡所有方法換晒自己既人入政府，方便控制晒成個香港既所有運作<br />\n更加唔會容許公務員有反對既聲音存在<br />\n睇唔到你名唔緊要，有殺錯冇放過直接換走晒所有香港既公務員就一了百了<br />\n<br />\n所以唔該你地唔好再縮<br />\n認認真真去諗下<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無限期罷工</span>呢個方法<br />\n一齊抗爭到底<br />\n如果你決定繼續縮唔緊要<br />\n當有一日我講既野成真果陣唔好後悔<br />\n<br />\n到時我應該係赤柱定唔知邊個集中營入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf29a7ae01823379a2f114a008756e9950e45503","tid":1378720,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我有權唔解鎖 我要搵律師 我唔簽任何文件 我唔信任何警察 我要警誡記錄 我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所 我唔舒服要去醫院 我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你</code></pre>"},{"pid":"535890dab24d3011cee81accb1bf844b8b879069","tid":1378720,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8246a1d3035699e1d4b881e16b7caf6ab521545","tid":1378720,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"好好諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71730783a98b61f1c5ffedc7de9007d6b7ec7511","tid":1378720,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"冇人睇到?咁我訓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04aa0e35e8a503daeac8fc87c80842bf810ddf68","tid":1378720,"uid":259675,"like":